                <mxCell id="83" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Financial Data&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Real-time retrieval of cost and consumption data from ERP/accounting systems&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;API pulls include meter IDs, billing periods, and cost centers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;All data extracted here is loaded “as-is” into the Raw Data Layer before any cleaning or transformation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 8;fillColor=#dae8fc;" parent="1" vertex="1">
